```class Solution {
    public String crackSafe(int n, int k) {
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {
            sb.append(String.valueOf(k - 1));
        }
        String prefix = sb.toString();
        for (int i = 0; i < k; i++) {
            sb.append(i);
        }
        return prefix + sb.toString();
    }
}```
